title: Youth unemployment rate in Ghana in 2019
summary: In general Youth unemployment rate has stayed the same over the Year.
Youth unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2012.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2011 and 2012.
Maximum Youth unemployment rate, about 12.55 was reported at Year 2012
Minimum Youth unemployment rate about 12.17 was reached at Year 2011
